OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FAlmost 500-mile-long       
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Flightning bolt crossed     
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Fthree US states            
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, An almost 500-mile long bolt of        
OL,6, lightning that lit up the sky across   
OL,7, three US states has set a new world    
OL,8, record for longest flash, scientists   
OL,9, have confirmed.                        
OL,11,FThe lightning bolt, extended a total of
OL,12,F477.2 miles (768 km) and spread across 
OL,13,FMississippi, Louisiana, and Texas.     
OL,15,FThe previous record was 440.6 miles    
OL,16,F(709 km) and recorded in Brazil in     
OL,17,F2018.                                  
OL,19,FLightning rarely extends over 10 miles 
OL,20,Fand usually lasts under a second.      
